item.title: This will make you successful
item.description:
This will make you successful

You are your biggest investment. Don't be cheap when it comes to education, health and self-improvement. Continuous improvement is of paramount importance when it comes to your success in business or in life in general.

item.title: Bad behaviour
item.description:
Bad behaviour

Oddly enough, it isn't the truly terrible employees who cause the real problems. Whether clearly incompetent or unbelievably lazy, they're easy to spot. So although it's never fun to fire anyone, at least you know there's a problem - and you can quickly let the person go and move on.
